									<a name="#faq1"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">What is the Sarbanes-Oxley Act?</SPAN>
									<br>
									<br>
									Congress passed the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002 in response to the auditing 
									scandals at major U.S. companies like Enron and Worldcom. The law is designed 
									to ensure that company officials behave responsibly. One of the requirements of 
									Sarbanes-Oxley is that employees who have information of financial misconduct 
									can anonymously send that information to independent Audit Committees, or to 
									outside authorities and the media.
									<br>
									<br>
									<center><a href="#top">top</a></center>
									<br>
									<br>
									<a name="#faq2"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">What is TellSafe?</SPAN>
									<br>
									<br>
									TellSafe is an independent company with a unique service that allows employees 
									to make anonymous reports to their Audit Committees regarding financial 
									misconduct.
									<br>
									<br>
									<center><a href="#top">top</a></center>
									<br>
									<br>
									<a name="#faq3"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">What is Compliant™?</SPAN>
									<br>
									<br>
									Compliant™ is the name of TellSafe's application that provides for anonymous 
									employee submissions and retrieval of those submissions by Audit Committees.
									<br>
									<br>
									<center><a href="#top">top</a></center>
									<br>
									<br>
									<a name="#faq4"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">How secure is the TellSafe site?</SPAN>
									<br>
									<br>
									We pride ourselves on our site security. <a href="..\main\security.aspx">Click here</a> to 
									read more about site security.<br>
									<a href="..\main\privacy.aspx">Click here</a> to view our Privacy Policy.
									<br>
									<br>
									<center><a href="#top">top</a></center>
									<br>
									<br>
									<a name="#faq5"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">What will TellSafe and Compliant™ mean to 
										me?</SPAN>
									<br>
									<br>
									By subscribing to Compliant™, you will immediately be in compliance with 
									Section 301 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act. As a Subscriber to Compliant™, you can 
									safeguard employees while giving your Audit Committee the opportunity to 
									investigate alleged financial misconduct.
									<br>
									<br>
									<center><a href="#top">top</a></center>
									<br>
									<br>
									<a name="#faq6"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">How long has TellSafe been in business?</SPAN>
									<br>
									<br>
									TellSafe, LLC was founded in 2003 in answer to the Sarbanes-Oxley Act. TellSafe 
									is completely funded by its partners. <a href="..\main\about.aspx">Click here</a> to 
									learn more about us.
									<br>
									<br>
									<center><a href="#top">top</a></center>
									<br>
									<br>
									<a name="#faq8"></a><SPAN CLASS="adH1">How much is a subscription?</SPAN>
